  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">The mean of the list of numbers above is what fraction of the sum of the five numbers?</p>\n",
  "answerOptions": [],
  "keys": [],
  "rationale": "<p>The correct answer is <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"one fifth\"></span>. The mean of the list of numbers is found by dividing the sum of the numbers by the number of values in the list. Since there are 5 numbers in the list, the mean is <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"one fifth\"></span> of the sum of the numbers. Note that 1/5 and .2 are examples of ways to enter a correct answer.</p>\n",
